	<div itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Person" class="col-sm-8">

	<p>Hi there, my name is Hangwei QIAN (钱航薇). Currently I am a Wallenberg - NTU Presidential Postdoctoral Fellow in Nanyang Technological University, Singapore with Prof. Chunyan Miao. <!-- p class="lead" -->

    <p>My research interests are machine learning, kernel methods, transfer learning and human activity recognition. </p>
    		
    <p>I am open to collaboration. Please contact me if you are interested in working with me.</p>
    
    <p>I obtained my Ph.D. in School of Computer Science and Engineering at NTU, Singapore in 2020. I'm honored to work with <a href= "https://www3.ntu.edu.sg/home/sinnopan/" target="_blank">Professor Sinno Jialin Pan</a>. I received my B.E. from Automation, School of Information Science and Technology from<a href="http://en.ustc.edu.cn/" target = "_blank"> Univeristy of Science and Technology of China (USTC)</a> in 2015.</p>

	</div>
	
